lescope (LSST) design, and it can be extended to\nother telescopes. We expect that because of the comprehensive physics\nimplemented in PhoSim, it will be used by the community to plan future\nobservations, interpret detailed existing observations, and quantify\nsystematics related to various astronomical measurements. Future development\nand validation by comparisons with real data will continue to improve the\nfidelity and usability of the code.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Apr 2015 17:06:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-27"}
